{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "errorprobe-silent",
  "title": "ErrorProbe — Silent Containers",
  "description": "Surfaces containers that have stopped or sharply slowed their logging — a signal for hung, dead or severely throttled workloads that produce no errors yet are not healthy.",
  "tags": ["errorprobe"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-10m", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": ["30s", "1m", "5m"],
    "time_options": ["5m", "10m", "30m", "1h"]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### How to read this dashboard\n- **Left table** — log lines received in the **last 2 minutes** (current activity), sorted least-active first.\n- **Right table** — log lines received **2–10 minutes ago** (recent baseline).\n- A container present in the right table but **absent from the left** has gone quiet — check `ep watch` or `ep status` for its infra state.\n- Containers with **zero logs in the entire 10-minute window** do not appear in either table. Use `ep status` to confirm they are still running.\n- The time-series at the bottom makes flatlines (dead containers) visually obvious."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Log Lines — Last 2 min (least active first)",
      "description": "Containers at the top are the quietest right now.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "errorprobe-loki" },
      "options": {
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Lines", "desc": false }],
        "footer": { "show": false }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "auto", "displayMode": "auto" } },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Value" }, "properties": [{ "id": "displayName", "value": "Lines" }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Time" }, "properties": [{ "id": "custom.hidden", "value": true }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "container" }, "properties": [{ "id": "displayName", "value": "Container" }, { "id": "custom.width", "value": 220 }] }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (container) (count_over_time({container=~\".+\"} [2m]))",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{container}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [{ "id": "merge", "options": {} }]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Log Lines — 2–10 min ago (baseline)",
      "description": "Containers present here but absent from the left table may have gone silent since then.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "errorprobe-loki" },
      "options": {
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Lines", "desc": false }],
        "footer": { "show": false }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "auto", "displayMode": "auto" } },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Value" }, "properties": [{ "id": "displayName", "value": "Lines" }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Time" }, "properties": [{ "id": "custom.hidden", "value": true }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "container" }, "properties": [{ "id": "displayName", "value": "Container" }, { "id": "custom.width", "value": 220 }] }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (container) (count_over_time({container=~\".+\"} [8m] offset 2m))",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{container}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [{ "id": "merge", "options": {} }]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Log Rate per Container — 10-minute view",
      "description": "Lines dropping to zero and staying there are dead containers. A brief dip followed by recovery is a restart.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "errorprobe-loki" },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["last", "min", "mean"]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "spanNulls": false,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate({container=~\".+\"} [1m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{container}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
